{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-hackers-js","path":"/hackers/report-actions.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>There are 4 actions you can take on a report that you've submitted:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Add comment</li>\n<li>Self-close</li>\n<li>Request mediation</li>\n<li>Requesting Public Disclosure</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"commenting-and-closing-a-report\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#commenting-and-closing-a-report\" aria-label=\"commenting and closing a report permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Commenting and Closing a Report</h3>\n<p>You can dialogue with the program or triager and make notes about the report through adding comments. Additionally, you can self-close your own report and close it as N/A.</p>\n<p>To add comments or to close a report:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the bottom of the report you want to take action on.</li>\n<li>In the action picker above the comment box you can choose to <strong>Add comment</strong> or <strong>Close report</strong>.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34.400000000000006%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"report-actions-hacker-1\"\n        title=\"report-actions-hacker-1\"\n        src=\"/static/b2693d51525ae6b38028cbab459cdcaa/0b533/report-actions-hacker-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b2693d51525ae6b38028cbab459cdcaa/fac75/report-actions-hacker-1.png 125w,\n/static/b2693d51525ae6b38028cbab459cdcaa/63868/report-actions-hacker-1.png 250w,\n/static/b2693d51525ae6b38028cbab459cdcaa/0b533/report-actions-hacker-1.png 500w,\n/static/b2693d51525ae6b38028cbab459cdcaa/1d69c/report-actions-hacker-1.png 750w,\n/static/b2693d51525ae6b38028cbab459cdcaa/00d43/report-actions-hacker-1.png 1000w,\n/static/b2693d51525ae6b38028cbab459cdcaa/016a8/report-actions-hacker-1.png 1576w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n</ol>\n<p>When the report is in the triaged state, you can only add comments to the report.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 29.599999999999998%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"report-actions-hacker-2\"\n        title=\"report-actions-hacker-2\"\n        src=\"/static/7c2c7b21aed6ffe465a5129bd42902f0/0b533/report-actions-hacker-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7c2c7b21aed6ffe465a5129bd42902f0/fac75/report-actions-hacker-2.png 125w,\n/static/7c2c7b21aed6ffe465a5129bd42902f0/63868/report-actions-hacker-2.png 250w,\n/static/7c2c7b21aed6ffe465a5129bd42902f0/0b533/report-actions-hacker-2.png 500w,\n/static/7c2c7b21aed6ffe465a5129bd42902f0/1d69c/report-actions-hacker-2.png 750w,\n/static/7c2c7b21aed6ffe465a5129bd42902f0/00d43/report-actions-hacker-2.png 1000w,\n/static/7c2c7b21aed6ffe465a5129bd42902f0/5df5d/report-actions-hacker-2.png 1572w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"request-mediation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#request-mediation\" aria-label=\"request mediation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Request Mediation</h3>\n<p>You can also request for mediation from HackerOne in extreme cases when all normal discussions with the team have been attempted and there has been no satisfactory resolution.</p>\n<p>To request mediation, select the <strong>Report abuse</strong> option, and select <strong>Report Mediation</strong>.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 10.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAbElEQVQI12WMywqEMBAE/f9PdMF1D5kJBEMiZLJ5tqNXD0VD0dTivYcxBveWUhBCgHNOHYGZ8Vc358QY48Xtc85gYv1axBixHBoiIlhrISJPVCQjpaQIaq1orb3ovcNq5LttWNcP9v2HM564AJiXmWAQG73NAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"report-actions-hacker-3\"\n        title=\"report-actions-hacker-3\"\n        src=\"/static/8429e0cb12357f3c6cd3668c2642f0a7/0b533/report-actions-hacker-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8429e0cb12357f3c6cd3668c2642f0a7/fac75/report-actions-hacker-3.png 125w,\n/static/8429e0cb12357f3c6cd3668c2642f0a7/63868/report-actions-hacker-3.png 250w,\n/static/8429e0cb12357f3c6cd3668c2642f0a7/0b533/report-actions-hacker-3.png 500w,\n/static/8429e0cb12357f3c6cd3668c2642f0a7/8ce52/report-actions-hacker-3.png 681w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"request-public-disclosure\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#request-public-disclosure\" aria-label=\"request public disclosure permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Request Public Disclosure</h3>\n<p>You can also request public disclosure for your closed reports by selecting <strong>Request public disclosure</strong>. The option is available in your action picker once the report has been closed.</p>\n<p>If the program requests for public disclosure, you'll have the option to <strong>Disclose publicly</strong> as well.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><i>Note: Public Disclosure is <strong>Not</strong> available for private programs.</i> </p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"title":"Report Actions","id":"hackers/report-actions","path":"/hackers/report-actions.html","description":null},"headings":[{"value":"Commenting and Closing a Report"},{"value":"Request Mediation"},{"value":"Request Public Disclosure"}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}